{"tid":374613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣綫故障 須額外行車時間","createTime":"2017-08-26T01:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T02:04:37.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4447b06b3733f2601e2186aba945120755c6505","tid":374613,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:26:47.000Z","msg":"荃灣綫額外行車時間<br />\n<br />\n此訊息發放時間 : 2017-08-26 09:19<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n荃灣綫列車預計需要額外行車時間，請為行程預留充裕時間。我們會盡快提供進一步消息。"},{"pid":"745a4f75d910320836eda11d17ea7db6ce39943e","tid":374613,"uid":29942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:29:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又壞"},{"pid":"310e43f084c8250207fd0d19cb61f42920ee684a","tid":374613,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:29:37.000Z","msg":"荃灣綫額外行車時間<br />\n<br />\n此訊息發放時間 : 2017-08-26 09:25<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於荔景站附近有信號故障，荃灣綫列車駛經美孚站至荔景站路段時需要慢駛，荃灣綫來往中環站及荃灣站的行車時間預計需要額外15-20分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣綫服務更改如下<br />\n中環站 往返<br />\n荃灣站<br />\n每5分鐘一班<br />\n<br />\n現時荃灣綫月台上的乘客較多，候車時間亦會較長。<br />\n請為行程預留充裕時間。<br />\n港鐵職員現正進行搶修工作。<br />\n如有不便，敬請見諒。"},{"pid":"447298aa27f619c695e579844f4d61282fdfb534","tid":374613,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:30:23.000Z","msg":"MTR Service Update&rlm; @mtrupdate  2m2 minutes ago<br />\nMore<br />\n 0918 荃灣綫荔景站訊號故障，服務嚴重受阻，可考慮其他交通工具.<br />\n<br />\nMTR Service Update&rlm; @mtrupdate  2m2 minutes ago<br />\nMore<br />\n 部分荃灣綫列車或會於中途站停止服務，以紓緩擠塞情況，請留意月台或車廂的廣播<br />\n<br />\n為盡快疏導乘客，控制中心亦會按實際情況，而適時加開空車"},{"pid":"67b1b91e468622fa8b480ffaef1008ab3ed8b119","tid":374613,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:32:41.000Z","msg":"有無咁廢，屌佢老母"},{"pid":"1699783428daf195357a68c3fdd98852cac96107","tid":374613,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:35:11.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，成鳩日壞。地鐵高層幾撚時死呀含家剷"},{"pid":"5a23c48c830930c31ea5a3d5c40793f3503b11d4","tid":374613,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:36:28.000Z","msg":"fuck"},{"pid":"76ba6063ac442d83b3a29b6b000431fed4e069c1","tid":374613,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:36:54.000Z","msg":"又壞咩"},{"pid":"3059fcfe25c37243d94de4b070d23bda91639b5a","tid":374613,"uid":29942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"每壞一次扣高層花紅就岩嫁啦"},{"pid":"4e1728b9a64276220852a813fd8023a798f3d1b1","tid":374613,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:37:37.000Z","msg":"只係多15-20分鐘，唔夠30分鐘姐係又唔駛罰。下年再加下價先"},{"pid":"5e6ec8b5f07302167f146a3910dd376fc3fc1bc2","tid":374613,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:38:41.000Z","msg":"馬屎坑：正常能量釋放"},{"pid":"691d9a08f979caef5aca951d5e2d8b0dd05010cd","tid":374613,"uid":82915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"又壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚野"},{"pid":"9f93e8f190958e223629983405a4a8904d18f768","tid":374613,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:41:35.000Z","msg":"又壞，有無咁撚廢啊"},{"pid":"65f8bac2fcf34982a47e1a0fd314cb1444c539d2","tid":374613,"uid":115525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:41:37.000Z","msg":"孔乙己Mode: 慢車不能算壞!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471c90baf88ebcc850796d18972226076cf98d36","tid":374613,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb68dd35eef3e4d